# <type>(<scope>): <short summary>
# │       │             │
# │       │             └─⫸ Summary in present tense. Not capitalized. No period at the end.
# │       │
# │       └─⫸ Commit Scope: routing|ui|store|auth|etc.
# │
# └─⫸ Commit Type: feat|fix|docs|style|refactor|test|chore
#
# Types:
# feat     ✨ A new feature
# fix      🐛 A bug fix
# docs     📝 Documentation only changes
# style    💄 Changes that do not affect the meaning of the code
# refactor ♻️  A code change that neither fixes a bug nor adds a feature
# test     ✅ Adding missing tests or correcting existing tests
# chore    🔧 Changes to the build process or auxiliary tools
#
# Example commit messages:
# feat(auth): add login form component
# fix(api): handle network errors in user service
# docs(readme): update installation guide
# style(components): improve button styling
# refactor(store): simplify user state management
# test(utils): add tests for date formatter
# chore(deps): update dependencies
